    #   The *dynamic* evolution of the textbook กรอบวัน (daily frame) 1000 points (fixed open±500 → actual 1~4h swing).
    #   Decision (between lock_min_hours~window_hours):
    #     (high-low)/low ≤ day_h4_atr_pct × max_atr_ratio  AND  both poles touched min_touches+ times = ping-pong lock
    #   Guard (when locked):
    #     inside the box (edge~1-edge) = block / near top (1-edge ~ 1) = SHORT only / near bottom (0 ~ edge) = LONG only
    #   Release: lock releases on box breakout (≥ breakout_pct) (breakout entry possible).
