    # ★★★ Phase 2 Conviction-refinement helpers (2026-05-11 owner 95%/98%, second step)
    # "this table's score = the system's eye" -- position precision + momentum concord
    # ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

    # ============================================================
    # ★ [2026-05-17 Phase 4 top-down 100-pt formula - 5 new helpers]
    #   plan: docs/plan_conviction_phase4_top_down_2026-05-17.md
    #   18 conditions = multi-TF alignment matrix + 4-TF change rate + RSI + S/R + Volume + existing ADX/MACD/BB/PA + time/coin + separate (Reentry/Context/MomRev)
