    # This agent's 9-day diagnosis: net_vs_fee 0.16x -> target 0.20~0.26x (1 week)
    # Complies with the 10 review items of this agent's letter #11 + 7 edge cases
    # Owner ① D paper_mode + ② A port to FOCUS + ③ A confirm 1-week paper
